elper\n│       └── utils.py                   # read_token_from_file() helper\n├── tests/\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── conftest.py\n│   ├── test_imports.py\n│   ├── test_exceptions.py\n│   └── test_utils.py\n├── design.md\n└── spec.md\n```\n\n### Key SDK Source Files (full content already shown above):\n\n1. **`AgentRuntimeClient`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/agent_runtime.py`):\n   - Constructor with `agent_name`, `namespace`, `router_url`, `verbose`, `session_id`, `timeout`, `connect_timeout`\n   - Resolves `router_url` from arg or `ROUTER_URL` env var\n   - Bootstraps session via `dp_client.bootstrap_session_id()` if `session_id` is None\n   - Context manager (`__enter__`/`__exit__`)\n   - `invoke(payload, timeout)` -- validates session, delegates to data plane, returns `resp.json()`\n   - `close()` -- delegates to `dp_client.close()`\n\n2. **`AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`):\n   - `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"`\n   - Constructs `base_url` via `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/agent-runtimes/{agent_name}/invocations/\")`\n   - `bootstrap_session_id()` -- GET base_url, read header, raise ValueError if missing\n   - `invoke(session_id, payload, timeout)` -- POST with session header + JSON body\n   - `close()` -- closes HTTP session\n\n---\n\n## 4. Existing Tests and Testing Patterns\n\n### SDK Tests (`python-sdk/tests/`)\n\n| File | Path | Pattern |\n|------|------|---------|\n| `test_imports.py` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/tests/test_imports.py` | Class-based tests (`TestImports`, `TestPublicExports`), simple assertions |\n| `test_exceptions.py` | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_202604